# App_Data: ignore runtime/generated content but track committed files
# By default, App_Data contains uploaded/generated files — add specific
# exceptions below if you need to track certain files in App_Data.
# Example: !App_Data/some-committed-file.xml

# wkhtmltopdf binaries in App_Data (these are large native binaries —
# consider whether they should be tracked or installed via a build script)
# If you want to KEEP them tracked, uncomment the line below:
# !**/App_Data/wkhtmltopdf/**

*.pdf
*.docx
*.doc
*.pptx
*.mp4
*.rar
*.csv
*.xlsx
*.xls